Dalibor Bagarić sraral hya'ga sisyow na NBA, wal malaxmisoq qaniy la. kawas te 1980, byacing te 2 ro 7 ryax qo hintgan nya, kinholan nya ga West Germany, hiya ga mnanak na ppzoy mari waya, ro sqoliq ka ppkal mari waya. 216 konbon kinwagiq nya, 132 konkin kin'sow nya, hiya ga qotox nqo spzyang blaq na ppzoy mari NBA. kawas 2000 mnwayaw ppzoy mari ga, mzyop sqo te qotox lahoy ro te magal sqoliq, galon nqo Chicago Bolls. cinkholan sa knita' sa brbiro' Lists of National Basketball Association players
